      <title>逆势印度基金经理对债券追逐者发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/contrarian-indian-fund-manager-has-a-warning-for-bond-chasers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位印度基金经理逆势大幅降低了其旗舰债券基金的平均期限，进一步缩短了久期，因为市场预期央行不会先于全球同行降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/contrarian-indian-fund-manager-has-a-warning-for-bond-chasers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
