    <item>
      <title>权力平衡 04/25/24</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-26/balance-of-power-04-25-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《权力平衡》聚焦于政治与全球商业的交叉点。今天的节目中，伊利诺伊州民主党众议员拉贾·克里希纳莫蒂谈及美国国务卿布林肯访华，表示布林肯此访对美中关系具有建设性意义。卡多佐法学院教授、纽约南区前联邦检察官杰西卡·罗斯剖析了美国最高法院就前总统特朗普豁免权主张举行的听证会辩论。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-26/balance-of-power-04-25-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡房价增长放缓，市场降温导致租金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/singapore-home-price-growth-slows-rents-decline-as-market-cools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着新加坡房地产繁荣开始失去动力，上个季度新加坡房价增长放缓，租金下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/singapore-home-price-growth-slows-rents-decline-as-market-cools</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:40:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔将秘鲁评级下调至 BBB-，展望稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/peru-downgraded-to-bbb-by-s-p-outlook-stable-lvfxhakl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级周四将秘鲁的长期外币主权信用评级从“BBB”下调至“BBB-”，原因是国会分散和政府有限的政治资本打压私营部门投资情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/peru-downgraded-to-bbb-by-s-p-outlook-stable-lvfxhakl</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国关键通胀数据公布之前，石油价格将每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀数据公布之前，油价每周上涨，这可能为货币政策的未来路径提供进一步线索，从而影响对包括原油等大宗商品在内的风险资产的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 23:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行：市场结束前，亚洲科技股上涨，日元区间波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市收盘后，微软公司和 Alphabet 公司公布了出色的盈利报告，亚洲科技股随之上涨。在日本央行做出政策决定之前，日元窄幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 22:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于价格粘性影响美联储路径，美国债券引领全球抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/treasuries-hold-losses-after-seven-year-sale-meets-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债收益率升至 2024 年高点，因为有证据表明美国价格压力巨大，使人们对美联储今年晚些时候开始降息的能力产生怀疑。全球债券也出现了抛售潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/treasuries-hold-losses-after-seven-year-sale-meets-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 17:15:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
